  BinktermPHP is an open source modern web-based BBS and FidoNet 
  mailer — a love letter to the golden age of bulletin board 
  systems, rebuilt for the web with PHP, PostgreSQL, and Bootstrap. 

  If you grew up on BBSes, or you're just drawn to niche protocol
  work and community-driven software, this might be your kind of 
  project.
  

